{"tid":337583,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"今日做完smile矯視 你問我答","createTime":"2017-07-27T12:14:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T12:25:43.000Z","uid":8754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad38eaf622774e6215c8cefc3a64a6d8ad407438","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b6d7161fcc8ca9c7016a374ce6e8eeb1271481","tid":337583,"uid":105858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:16:41.000Z","msg":"做咗幾錢？"},{"pid":"caa2b443541c5563eeab5879701fe6a1b603198e","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:17:06.000Z","msg":"$26100 匯豐卡做緊promo"},{"pid":"f3f993d5349a0400517bd812f503bcf5416e9143","tid":337583,"uid":73349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:18:12.000Z","msg":"感覺點？"},{"pid":"d31f76b6a21300d6993aa3f36e15f1c9d5bba0b7","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:19:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感覺點？</blockquote><br />\n做個時唔痛既 麻醉藥過左有d un住既感覺<br />\n一做完就清晒 但怕光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而睇近野矇矇地"},{"pid":"ac965396bbda35269e899c73deff761dc1e4b62c","tid":337583,"uid":51411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"過程係點？耐唔耐？驚唔驚副作用"},{"pid":"24dc38c854f82c4ef1ae425fb6ca2272b1238c6f","tid":337583,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:35:37.000Z","msg":"一年後再開post 睇下有無後遺症"},{"pid":"5d5b96de823db06fc4dccfb898829d8754eae5a8","tid":337583,"uid":9470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:35:42.000Z","msg":"散光做有無用？有無話最少要有幾多度近視先可以做smile?"},{"pid":"e026e642a0cf18848370c60c88a24fb43d5bd3d9","tid":337583,"uid":100597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:35:47.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛排期"},{"pid":"e02e68a71ef8c1dd0db9825095b172cfda01cc32","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過程係點？耐唔耐？驚唔驚副作用</blockquote><br />\n首先去間房滴麻醉藥水 著保護衣物<br />\n等左20分鐘到 <br />\n之後入房 坐落部機到 做完右眼到左眼<br />\n醫生會搵野撐開右眼 之後叫你望住綠燈<br />\n之後就有層霧遮住隻眼 23秒到<br />\n之後醫生會用野夾走塊lens 但過程無感覺<br />\n你都睇唔到佢用咩夾 整係感覺到有人搞你隻眼<br />\n之後左眼 兩隻眼夾埋10分鐘到<br />\n做完拎眼藥水走得<br />\n<br />\n其實我都驚副作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過見咁多人做完都無事<br />\n應該ok既"},{"pid":"862a5e99a817312e5f7b299a4f537204865e4149","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:41:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一年後再開post 睇下有無後遺症</blockquote><br />\n希望無 細妹做左兩年都好好"},{"pid":"1b80ffaef04d496214f7a390871be1a760629e93","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>散光做有無用？有無話最少要有幾多度近視先可以做smile?</blockquote><br />\n散光都做到 我隻眼都25度散光<br />\nSmile無限既 近視1000度以下 散光好似400度以下就得<br />\n我做前一日有姑娘檢查隻眼 一般只要lens夠厚 眼正常大細就得"},{"pid":"7fb6b8794e8ad542e8794e0dfe352252ff57064c","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:44:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>駛唔駛排期</blockquote><br />\n唔駛 我帶開con<br />\n就要等一星期做檢查 無帶開直情可以book聽日檢查<br />\n後日手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349f1a291e662371664cb1c362a77af8e5144338","tid":337583,"uid":47177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:27:54.000Z","msg":"邊度做？"},{"pid":"bc5718b34b05b38ca24707e3f722f7457f9bbf0e","tid":337583,"uid":126690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05688b449fa7fb5320222d749732660e54e9a7a5","tid":337583,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:37:22.000Z","msg":"近視1200<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咪做唔到"},{"pid":"89435703c0d375fec8ab2d1df9a252961fc8ab3b","tid":337583,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:37:50.000Z","msg":"等果一星期係咪唔可以帶con?<br />\n<br />\n同埋做緊果陣時係咪黑曬睇唔到野？"},{"pid":"03eefb136ca0490ccc81ffc41ba441151035d42d","tid":337583,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:38:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近視1200<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咪做唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做lasik la"},{"pid":"608f05a6d5030937cbefc57984fe21dfe42583b7","tid":337583,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>近視1200<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咪做唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做lasik la</blockquote><br />\n唔好風險大，外國有人因為後遺症患左情緒病，之後自殺"},{"pid":"7128afac5a19e3410b78ab15ab0564a1043b696f","tid":337583,"uid":20352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:42:11.000Z","msg":"諗住等多5年睇下後遺症嚴唔嚴重先做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4cd66bca0da8ff8cc97b068a827eef7ad751d0","tid":337583,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:45:11.000Z","msg":"20年無後遺症先做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a485613d5f216546e2c669800e4a18fd72914f8d","tid":337583,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:45:11.000Z","msg":"20年無後遺症先做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86d9d81d505bff8a356fa0898e57b3f6fce15d3","tid":337583,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:48:27.000Z","msg":"都係個句啦..d視光師自己都帶眼鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ac35d52d2d2d5f76dcdb5591ea1f7f2843dd28","tid":337583,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:51:32.000Z","msg":"smile應該ok嘅"},{"pid":"9cddf95dad1ff41af0dcce3b238a44c248314fb1","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:22:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊度做？</blockquote><br />\n惠豐個間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"886ab6056f74bc0581c240e8830597d329194561","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下星期五做<br />\n巴打做之前驚唔驚會盲？</blockquote><br />\n驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過好似話無致盲個案<br />\n99.99成功<br />\n有3000分之1既機會矯唔晒<br />\n要再翻做"},{"pid":"acf576e3dc6c8744f40e07f74897ae3e695176d7","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近視1200<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咪做唔到</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要做lasik 舊個隻<br />\n最好問問醫生"},{"pid":"28b5dee531bb42555643a74c1dcd007390ff95ec","tid":337583,"uid":123632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:23:56.000Z","msg":"我都係呢間做完 一個月過左但唔清哂<br />\n仲有25度近視50度散光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最少唔洗帶眼鏡既"},{"pid":"3efeac4210c81714bfa93d082dcea3dde7d159e0","tid":337583,"uid":2153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:24:28.000Z","msg":"就黎死架喇你仲答"},{"pid":"15be50022f0d4071b0da83cbf9e4b56f0a3abd74","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等果一星期係咪唔可以帶con?<br />\n<br />\n同埋做緊果陣時係咪黑曬睇唔到野？</blockquote><br />\n係呀 1day con要停一星期<br />\n帶硬con要停一個月<br />\n做緊唔係黑晒 見到綠色光 同埋唔係黑 但有霧咁既感覺<br />\n見到醫生既儀器架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94a98c72a12eff3c436042d29f551534e3ec2ff","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"