df915556635377","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係呢間做完 一個月過左但唔清哂<br />\n仲有25度近視50度散光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最少唔洗帶眼鏡既</blockquote><br />\n一個月都未清晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好嚇我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗霧氣都清哂 係真係清唔哂個度數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊位醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都可以唔駛再用眼鏡都好啦"},{"pid":"c8a7001970a1639084978a3b7413aff3ae340275","tid":337583,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:20:30.000Z","msg":"我做完半年, 近視0 散光20 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edac78a9ab41d046f3abbddc085c5aa97321afe4","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我做完半年, 近視0 散光20 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恭喜巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424ee95babf91f2cc36c1fcc87577aef6d0ede20","tid":337583,"uid":55593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:22:16.000Z","msg":"有近視同老花做唔做得?"},{"pid":"1802a695eee1e972c3ff3ec8823545549bb99c5b","tid":337583,"uid"