":"2017-07-31T05:36:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係呢間做完 一個月過左但唔清哂<br />\n仲有25度近視50度散光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最少唔洗帶眼鏡既</blockquote><br />\n佢個問答入面寫加減75度係正常喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">激光矯視後可回復零度近視嗎?<br />\n<br />\n有很多患者以為矯視後一定會達致零度近視，甚比配戴眼鏡或隱型眼鏡有更佳的視力。這是錯誤的觀念。<br />\n矯視成功標準:<br />\n如達到矯視前定立的目標度數的＋/－75度之內屬成功; 低於＋/－75度屬正常視力。<br />\n據文獻統計，矯視後3個月度數＋/－100度以內的成功率接近100%；<br />\n其中97%約在＋/－50度<br />\n若矯視後度數超＋/－100度，可以進行增進療程(Enhancement)改善</span>"},{"pid":"4531a722639ef0a86ea7dad541743bc329b0449b","tid":337583,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T05:39:21.000Z","msg":"其實係咪間間都差唔多，有冇話邊間口碑好<br />\n安全少出事"},{"pid":"8b822b7f9c3e469bd655cabc3c9d0fac778cbefe","tid":337583,"uid":69893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T05:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>匯豐有冇得分期?</blockquote><br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你分期做幾錢？上網睇冇免息分期嘅"},{"pid":"3fa5eb50a5184a08a64d539ae0885633eed3b918","tid":337583,"uid":44504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:40:04.000Z","msg":"幾時有後遺症"},{"pid":"cbe43fcffc46b09938fa3233daa2313e60815814","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:34:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪間間都差唔多，有冇話邊間口碑好<br />\n安全少出事</blockquote><br />\n搵d有名人做既個心定d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de32afd27534148f4718d7915738e8064cb569c","tid":337583,"uid":8754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>匯豐有冇得分期?</blockquote><br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你分期做幾錢？上網睇冇免息分期嘅</blockquote><br />\n有架 去到間野有寫<br />\n不過分期好似28000<br />\n我一筆過俾"},{"pid":"3688c178131a9e3f045d7317ed6475f0